{"name": "nomad-media-cli", "metadata": {"name": "nomad-media-cli", "version": "0.0.1a5", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["click", "nomad-media-pip", "platformdirs"], "summary": "Nomad Media Cli", "upload_time": 1733191446}, "documentation": ["# Nomad Media CLI Tool\n\nCommand line interface for managing Nomad Media media assets.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install nomad-media-cli\n```\n\n## Configuration\n- Default config location: %APPDATA%\\Local\\nomad_media_cli\\config.json\n- Custom config location: Use --config-path option\n\n## Commands\n\n### init\nInitializes CLI configuration\n\nOptions:\n- `--service-api-url`: API endpoint URL (required)\n- `--api-type`: API type [admin|portal]\n- `--debug-mode`: Enable debug logging [true|false]\n- `--singleton`: Enable singleton mode [true|false]\n\n### list-config-path\nLists the path of the config\n\n### update-config\nUpdates CLI configuration\n\nOptions:\n- `--service-api-url`: API endpoint URL\n- `--api-type`: API type [admin|portal]\n- `--debug-mode`: Enable debug logging [true|false]\n- `--singleton`: Enable singleton mode [true|false]\n\n### list-assets\nList assets by ID or path\n\nOptions:\n- `--id`: Asset UUID, collection ID, or saved search ID.\n- `--path`: Object key path (format: bucket::path). \"::\" is required if bucket is not set. Can set bucket with set-bucket.\n\n### upload-assets\nUploads an asset to nomad (next release)\n\nOptions:\n- `-r`: Recursive upload.\n- `--id`: Asset UUID, collection ID, or saved search ID.\n- `--path`: Object key path (format: bucket::path). \"::\" is required if bucket is not set. Can set bucket with set-bucket.\n\n### list-buckets\nLists all of the buckets\n\n### set-bucket\nSet bucket for user in config. Used for path.\n\nOptions:\n- `--bucket`: Name of the bucket to set in config.\n\n### list-tags\nLists all of the tags\n\n### set-tag\nSet the tag(s) for user in config.\n\nOptions:\n- `--tag`: Name of the tag(s) to set in config. Use multiple flags for multiple tags.\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "nomad_media_cli.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nomad_media_cli.utils.get_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ctx", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nomad_media_cli.utils.initialize_sdk", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ctx", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "nomad_media_cli.commands.list_config_path", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nomad_media_cli.commands.list_config_path.list_config_path", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ctx", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["List the configuration path"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "nomad_media_cli.cli", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nomad_media_cli.cli.cli", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ctx", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "config_path", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Nomad Media CLI"]}], "variables": [{"name": "nomad_media_cli.cli.CONFIG_DIR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nomad_media_cli.cli.CONFIG_PATH", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "nomad_media_cli.commands.set_bucket", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nomad_media_cli.commands.set_bucket.set_bucket", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ctx", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "bucket", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Set the default bucket"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "nomad_media_cli.commands.init", "documentation": [], "functions": 